item.title: Uwe Lulis
item.description: Uwe Lulis is a German guitarist and the key member and producer of the heavy metal band Rebellion since 2000. He also played guitar in Grave Digger for about 13 years, and was co-writer of many songs during his time in the band. When he left Grave Digger he formed his band Rebellion together with ex-bassist of Grave Digger, Tomi Göttlich.
